OL,4,CStreet and Emmerdale crossover episode
OL,6,FITV is to air its first ever crossover
OL,7,Fbetween Coronation Street and
OL,8,FEmmerdale, with fans able to vote for
OL,9,Fthe characters they would like to see
OL,10,Fmeet and interact.
OL,12,FThe hour-long crossover episode will
OL,13,Fair in January 2026 as ITV and STV
OL,14,Fannounce a new hour of soap schedule,
OL,15,Fwhich will see half hour Emmerdale
OL,16,Fepisodes air at 8pm, followed by 30-
OL,17,Fminute episodes of Coronation Street
OL,18,Fat 8.30pm.
