OL,6,FProducers of the two soaps say the
OL,7,Fspecial episode will have "everlasting
OL,8,Fconsequences for everyone involved",
OL,9,Fsaying the two shows' universes in
OL,10,FManchester and Yorkshire had been
OL,11,Flinked in an "ingenious way".
OL,13,FThey say the episode will be self-
OL,14,Fcontained, but its events will have
OL,15,F"repercussions for both communities
OL,16,Fand see them linked forever as
OL,17,Ffamiliar faces depart and exciting new
OL,18,Fcharacters arrive into both soaps".
